    "name": "ITE5315 Assignment 2 - Restaurant Explorer - Yung-Lun Lee",
    "description": "01 Home Route: Tests the home page route.\n\n02 Get All Data: Retrieves all restaurant records from the dataset.\n\n03 Get One Valid Record: Tests req.params.id by retrieving a valid restaurant record.\n\n04 Get Invalid Record: Tests error handling when a restaurant ID does not exist.\n\n05 Search by Keyword: Tests req.query.keyword by searching restaurants by name.\n\n06 Filter by Category: Tests req.query.category by filtering restaurants by cuisine.\n\n07 Table View: Displays restaurant data using an EJS rendered table.\n\n08 Add Form Page: Displays the form used to add a new restaurant.\n\n09 Add New Restaurant - Valid POST: Tests form submission using valid restaurant data.\n\n10 Add New Restaurant - Invalid POST: Tests validation middleware using invalid form data.\n\n11 Wrong Route: Tests custom 404 error handling.",
